The paper deals with planning in nondeterministic domains, which is a common problem in artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of symbolic model checking techniques, which are commonly used in formal verification and logic, making cs.LO and cs.PL likely sub-categories as well. The paper also presents an algorithm and an implementation, which could fall under cs.DS and cs.SE respectively.
